Test to verify using Octo with Extended References

Remove names table from Octo, as we plan to add it, but to a different database
DROP TABLE
DROP TABLE

Create extended reference database with GLD extended.gld & load names into it

Set ^names(1) = "Extended|Reference"

Run a couple of queries to verify functionality and create AIM index
id|firstname|lastname
0|Zero|Cool
1|Extended|Reference
2|Cereal|Killer
3|Lord|Nikon
4|Joey|
5|Zero|Cool
(6 rows)
id|firstname|lastname
1|Extended|Reference
(1 row)

AIM Data in local DB (should be empty): 

AIM Data in Extended DB: 
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7="^names"
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(0)="*YottaDB*"
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(1)=1
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(2)="|"
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(2,"#",4)=""
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(2,"#Cool",0)=""
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(2,"#Cool",5)=""
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(2,"#Killer",2)=""
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(2,"#Nikon",3)=""
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(2,"#Reference",1)=""
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(3)="#01"
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(4)="#01"
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(5)=""
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(6)="+^names(sub1=*) -command=set -name=%ydbERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7S -xecute=<<"_$C(10)_" for i=2 set p=""#""_$piece($ztoldval,""|"",i),q=""#""_$piece($ztvalue,""|"",i) do"_$C(10)_" . if p'=q zkill ^|""$PWD/extended.gld""|%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(i,p,sub1) set ^|""$PWD/extended.gld""|%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(i,q,sub1)="""""_$C(10)_" . else  set:'($zlength(q)-1) ^|""$PWD/extended.gld""|%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(i,""#"",sub1)="""""_$C(10)
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(7)="+^names(sub1=*) -command=kill -name=%ydbERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7K -xecute=<<"_$C(10)_" do dft($reference) quit"_$C(10)_" if ^|""$PWD/extended.gld""|%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7"_$C(10)_"dft(var)"_$C(10)_" new sub,vard,vars,varsd,vsroot"_$C(10)_" set vard=$data(@var)"_$C(10)_" do:vard\10"_$C(10)_" . if $qlength(var) set vsroot=$zextract(var,1,$zlength(var)-1)_"","""_$C(10)_" . else  set vsroot=var_""("""_$C(10)_" . set vars=vsroot_""sub)"""_$C(10)_" . set sub="""" for  do  set sub=$order(@vars) quit:'$zlength(sub)"_$C(10)_" . . set varsd=$data(@vars)"_$C(10)_" . . if varsd\10 do dft(vsroot_$zwrite(sub)_"")"")"_$C(10)_" . . else  kill:varsd#10 @(vsroot_$zwrite(sub)_"")"")"_$C(10)_" zkill:vard#10 @var"_$C(10)_" quit"_$C(10)
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(8)="+^names(sub1=*) -command=zkill -name=%ydbERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7Z -xecute=""for i=2 zkill ^|""""$PWD/extended.gld""""|%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(i,""""#""""_$piece($ztoldval,""""|"""",i),sub1)"""
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(9)=1
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(10)=0
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7(12)="+^names -command=kill -name=%ydbERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC70 -xecute=<<"_$C(10)_" do dft($reference) quit"_$C(10)_" if ^|""$PWD/extended.gld""|%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7"_$C(10)_"dft(var)"_$C(10)_" new sub,vard,vars,varsd,vsroot"_$C(10)_" set vard=$data(@var)"_$C(10)_" do:vard\10"_$C(10)_" . if $qlength(var) set vsroot=$zextract(var,1,$zlength(var)-1)_"","""_$C(10)_" . else  set vsroot=var_""("""_$C(10)_" . set vars=vsroot_""sub)"""_$C(10)_" . set sub="""" for  do  set sub=$order(@vars) quit:'$zlength(sub)"_$C(10)_" . . set varsd=$data(@vars)"_$C(10)_" . . if varsd\10 do dft(vsroot_$zwrite(sub)_"")"")"_$C(10)_" . . else  kill:varsd#10 @(vsroot_$zwrite(sub)_"")"")"_$C(10)_" zkill:vard#10 @var"_$C(10)_" quit"_$C(10)
^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7("comment-2")="xref for table names column lastname"
^%ydbAIMDxref("^names","^%ydbAIMDERzGTIrQTVBoOhdanoKcC7")=""

